Aku di mana?

752
00:51:59,250 --> 00:52:00,840
Ini kamar Hill?

753
00:52:03,660 --> 00:52:06,330
North, kamu bikin aku kesel banget.

754
00:52:06,410 --> 00:52:08,130
Kenapa kamu lakukan itu?

755
00:52:08,230 --> 00:52:10,020
Kenapa kamu harus berkelahi sama mereka?

756
00:52:10,070 --> 00:52:12,280
Kamu tahu nggak, aku nelpon Ikkyu.

757
00:52:12,280 --> 00:52:14,350
Begitu dia bilang kamu ada masalah,

758
00:52:14,380 --> 00:52:16,190
aku khawatir banget sama kamu.

759
00:52:16,310 --> 00:52:19,670
Kapan sih kamu mau berhenti gegabah?

760
00:52:20,250 --> 00:52:22,010
Maaf.

761
00:52:22,120 --> 00:52:24,330
Lain kali aku bakal coba lebih tenang.

762
00:52:25,810 --> 00:52:28,720
Jangan berkelahi lagi nanti, ya.

763
00:52:29,460 --> 00:52:31,850
Iya, aku janji.

764
00:52:34,220 --> 00:52:36,530
Coba tenangin diri.

765
00:52:38,760 --> 00:52:40,720
Tapi menurutku,

766
00:52:40,720 --> 00:52:43,210
kamu pasti lama nggak mau minum lagi.

767
00:52:44,210 --> 00:52:45,430
Kenapa?

768
00:52:46,970 --> 00:52:49,530
Aku di mana, kau bisa kasih tahu?

769
00:52:51,330 --> 00:52:53,250
Ini rumah temannya Hill.

770
00:52:53,560 --> 00:52:54,810
Rumah Johan.

771
00:52:55,040 --> 00:52:56,620
Oh, Johan.

772
00:52:57,440 --> 00:53:00,730
Hah? Kok aku bisa di sini?

773
00:53:01,340 --> 00:53:04,680
Waktu Ikkyu bilang kamu bermasalah,

774
00:53:04,680 --> 00:53:06,050
aku nggak tahu harus apa.

775
00:53:06,080 --> 00:53:10,980
Jadi aku telepon Hill. Katanya dia urus.

776
00:53:15,910 --> 00:53:18,280
Aku angkat telepon dulu.

777
00:53:18,400 --> 00:53:19,390
Oke.

778
00:53:24,000 --> 00:53:25,620
Bro, jadi sebenarnya ada apa?

779
00:53:25,690 --> 00:53:28,690
Aku gimana sampai sini? Dia di mana?

780
00:53:28,840 --> 00:53:32,040
Dia kerja dulu, mungkin sebentar lagi pulang.

781
00:53:35,755 --> 00:53:36,750
Lepasin aku.

782
00:53:36,770 --> 00:53:38,750
Kataku, jangan bikin dia sakit hati.

783
00:53:41,120 --> 00:53:42,890
Astaga, jangan-jangan aku...

784
00:53:43,150 --> 00:53:45,430
Kemarin aku muntahin dia?

785
00:53:46,210 --> 00:53:47,200
Sekarang kamu ingat?

786
00:53:47,660 --> 00:53:49,680
Sepertinya dia juga marah sama kamu.

787
00:53:50,230 --> 00:53:54,590
Aku cuma ingat potongan-potongan.

788
00:53:55,210 --> 00:53:56,590
Tapi, bro...

789
00:53:57,340 --> 00:54:00,760
Aku nggak paham kenapa dia yang jemputku.

790
00:54:00,940 --> 00:54:03,520
Iya, pas dia bilang bakal urus itu,

791
00:54:03,920 --> 00:54:06,770
aku juga nggak ngira Johan yang jemput kamu.

792
00:54:07,390 --> 00:54:10,740
Kamu bilang sempat telepon Ikkyu, kan?

793
00:54:10,750 --> 00:54:11,920
Iya.

794
00:54:12,140 --> 00:54:13,920
Aku telepon dia.

795
00:54:25,560 --> 00:54:29,540
Ini HP-ku? Kok jadi begini?

796
00:54:30,330 --> 00:54:31,680
Aku nggak tahu.

797
00:54:31,980 --> 00:54:34,640
Nggak bisa dinyalain sama sekali.

798
00:54:34,920 --> 00:54:38,120
Pas Johan kasih ke aku, udah gini.

799
00:54:39,470 --> 00:54:41,450
Pasti dia yang bikin.

800
00:54:43,830 --> 00:54:45,050
Kenapa dia lakukan itu?

801
00:54:45,100 --> 00:54:47,120
Katamu dia kayaknya marah sama aku, kan?

802
00:54:47,170 --> 00:54:49,390
Lihat, nggak nyala sama sekali, kan?

803
00:54:49,580 --> 00:54:51,830
Parah banget.

804
00:54:53,080 --> 00:54:54,870
Emang aku salah apa ke dia?

805
00:54:55,070 --> 00:54:56,850
Kok dia sampai begitu ke aku?

806
00:54:57,800 --> 00:54:59,620
Kamu sih memang banyak ulah.

807
00:55:01,060 --> 00:55:03,410
- Aku apain? - Nih, lihat.

808
00:55:03,430 --> 00:55:06,610
Makanya kamu jadi ogah minum lama.

809
00:55:13,040 --> 00:55:14,280
Apa ini?

810
00:55:20,640 --> 00:55:21,880
Ter

811
00:55:26,220 --> 00:55:27,510
Iya, Ayah.

812
00:55:27,560 --> 00:55:29,510
Akhir pekan ini aku pulang.

813
00:55:30,240 --> 00:55:32,030
Oke, sampai jumpa.

814
00:55:36,000 --> 00:55:37,910
- Sudah selesai kerja? - Iya.

815
00:55:39,470 --> 00:55:41,250
Dia sudah bangun?

816
00:55:41,310 --> 00:55:43,610
Iya, dia sama Ter di dalam.

817
00:55:44,950 --> 00:55:46,290
Tunggu.

818
00:55:47,160 --> 00:55:49,450
Jangan-jangan kamu mau aneh-aneh ya.

819
00:56:13,630 --> 00:56:15,450
Maaf soal semalam.

820
00:56:15,940 --> 00:56:18,150
Terima kasih banyak.

821
00:56:18,390 --> 00:56:20,170
Aku juga minta maaf.

822
00:56:20,500 --> 00:56:21,570
Kamu muntahin aku semalam.

823
00:56:24,050 --> 00:56:24,720
Iya.

824
00:56:24,820 --> 00:56:26,980
Nggak apa-apa, cukup bayar aja.

825
00:56:27,740 --> 00:56:28,890
Bayar?

826
00:56:29,290 --> 00:56:30,890
Ganti rugi yang kamu bikin.

827
00:56:36,820 --> 00:56:38,490
Semua harus kamu lunasi.

828
00:57:06,910 --> 00:57:08,170
(Bocoran minggu depan)
Biaya rugi.

829
00:57:08,180 --> 00:57:09,910
Kamu wajib bayar semuanya.

830
00:57:09,930 --> 00:57:11,750
Bayar rugi aja aku nggak mampu.

831
00:57:11,810 --> 00:57:13,570
Dia nambahin bunga pula.

832
00:57:13,770 --> 00:57:15,630
Jadi aku harus cari kerja lagi.

833
00:57:16,170 --> 00:57:16,750
Oh.

834
00:57:17,050 --> 00:57:18,150
Aku nggak bakal nuntut kamu.

835
00:57:18,190 --> 00:57:20,430
Tapi kamu mau nurutin permintaanku?

836
00:57:21,010 --> 00:57:23,400
Katamu sudah suka lama, kan?

837
00:57:23,890 --> 00:57:24,610
Iya.

838
00:57:24,640 --> 00:57:26,610
Sebelum itu, kamu sudah kenal aku?

839
00:57:27,520 --> 00:57:28,610
Ter

840
00:57:29,250 --> 00:57:31,750
Boleh aku mulai lagi sama kamu?

